560
00:39:01,790 --> 00:39:02,930
It's okay.

561
00:39:02,930 --> 00:39:04,970
Come in. Come in and talk.

562
00:39:04,970 --> 00:39:07,350
No, no. We'll talk outside.

563
00:39:07,350 --> 00:39:09,430
I just need a moment.

