00:39:11,650 --> 00:39:13,880
Come in, Assistant Manager Seo.

565
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:22,280
Come in.

566
00:39:24,500 --> 00:39:26,590
Over here.

567
00:39:30,230 --> 00:39:33,690
