00:43:41,670 --> 00:43:43,990
He went out for work.

618
00:43:45,280 --> 00:43:49,230
Ah, I'm so tired. This work life really isn't for me.

619
00:43:49,230 --> 00:43:52,800
You're coming here empty-handed, so I wonder why you're tired.

620
00:43:52,800 --> 00:43:57,880
Sunbae, work isn't always done at the desk at the workplace.

621
00:43:57,880 --> 00:43:59,690
I just had a meal with Hye Rin.

622
00:43:59,690 --> 00:44:03,070
I told you to help out So Yeong since the samples are coming in today.

623
00:44:03,070 --> 00:44:06,390
All of this happened because I was trying to help Jeong So Yeong.

624
00:44:06,390 --> 00:44:10,140
If you all understood how big a sacrifice I'm making right now,

625
00:44:10,140 --> 00:44:14,230
you'll revalue my love for this team and this company.

626
00:44:14,230 --> 00:44:18,080
- We're missing one thing. I'll go check and bring it. 
 - Okay.

627
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:20,480
What are you doing?

