00:44:31,220 --> 00:44:33,980
Give it to me. I'll bring it.

630
00:44:35,890 --> 00:44:38,150
It's fine. I'll do it.

631
00:44:38,150 --> 00:44:40,550
I said I'll do it.

632
00:44:41,290 --> 00:44:43,720
I won't say anything about you coming to work as a hobby,

633
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:46,090
but I'd like it if you didn't use me as an excuse.

634
00:44:46,090 --> 00:44:49,130
It's offensive that someone, who thinks living life is the easiest thing because he will become an assistant manager

635
00:44:49,130 --> 00:44:52,240
and then a senior manager when the time is right, is using me, who works hard, as an excuse.

636
00:44:52,240 --> 00:44:55,790
- Excuse me. 
 - I moved all of the boxes by myself.

637
00:44:55,790 --> 00:44:59,250
Isn't it embarrassing to take the credit for other's hard work?

