00:46:35,790 --> 00:46:37,460
   

659
00:46:39,550 --> 00:46:41,550
Awesome!

660
00:46:42,680 --> 00:46:45,690
- Great! 
 - All right, let's get busy again.

661
00:46:45,690 --> 00:46:47,200
- Yes! 
 - Yes!

662
00:46:47,200 --> 00:46:49,360
Let's go!

663
00:46:49,360 --> 00:46:51,370
Here.

664
00:46:52,370 --> 00:46:56,300
Did you come here today to ask me to go easy on her again?

665
00:46:56,300 --> 00:46:58,770
That'd be nice.

