00:46:58,770 --> 00:47:01,990
But I really did want to eat with you.

667
00:47:01,990 --> 00:47:04,990
It'll get cold. Hurry and eat.

668
00:47:06,760 --> 00:47:14,110
Oh, and... I'm going to start a new job.

669
00:47:14,110 --> 00:47:15,600
What job?

